quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  89,1,"Mi woo…óndirii Fajira."
  89,2,"Mi woo…óndirii bal…óe sappa."
  89,3,"Mi woo…óndirii kala ko …óimmita e ko teel…ói."
  89,4,"Mi woo…óndarii jehma si mbo arii e ni…ď…ďidde."
  89,5,"Mbele ina e ndee woo…óndoore ja…ďnoore joom hakkille."
  89,6,"Mbele a yi'aani na joom ma wa…ói Aad en."
  89,7,"Irama joom doos…óe."
  89,8,"Mbo hono mum tagaaka e lesdi."
  89,9,"E Samuud …ďeen se'ek…ďe kaa∆īe to caatngol."
  89,10,"E Fir'awna joom peŇč…óe."
  89,11,"∆Āeen bewnoo…ďe to lesdi."
  89,12,"∆Āe kebbini e hendi bonan'nde."
  89,13,"Joom ma yuppi e ma…ď…ďe lepte ca…ótu…óe."
  89,14,"Koom ma na tommbii…ďe."
  89,15,"Tawi ko ne…ď…ó…óaŇčke si joom makko jarabiimo mbo o teddani mbo o neemini mbo o wiat joom am teddinii kam."
  89,16,"Si tawii noon o jaribiimo mbo o faa…óni arsuko makko o wi'a joom am hoynii kam."
  89,17,"Ala wona noon, ko woni ko on teddintaana baaya."
  89,18,"On ndeer…óiŇčtaa e √Īammiingol miskiino."
  89,19,"Ho…óon √Īaama ndonu √Īaamgol ca…ótungol."
  89,20,"Ho…óon nji…ói jawdi ji…ógol ca…ótungol."
  89,21,"Ala …óuum haanaani, si lesdi ndii dimmbaama dimmbugol."
  89,22,"Joom ma ardi e maleykaaji hi…ói mba…ói saffeeji."
  89,23,"jahanama addee √Īande heen ne…ó…óo siftoro kono hol ko ciftorgol nafata."